## 存数据：sessionStorageSet

![](data:image/png;base64,)

    
    
    cancel() {
            sessionStorage.setItem("sysRoleUserPage",this.page);
            this.$router.go(-1)
          },

## 取数据：sessionStorageGet

![](data:image/png;base64,)

    
    
    var pageRoleUser = sessionStorage.getItem("sysRoleUserPage");

## 删除某项缓存数据：sessionStorageRemove

![](data:image/png;base64,)

    
    
    ​
    sessionStorage.removeItem("sysRolePage");
    sessionStorage.removeItem("sysRoleUserPage");
    
    ​

## 清除本地所有存储数据：sessionStorageClear

![](data:image/png;base64,)

    
    
    sessionStorage.clear();
